		- magazine *
		- servicesblog *

	* Mismatched, CN: *.wordpress.com


	Partially covered subdomains:

		- investors	(→ investor.shareholder.com)


	Fully covered subdomains:

		- (www.)	(^ → www)
		- academy
		- access
		- (www.)apac	(^ → www)
		- ar
		- archive
		- at
		- au
		- be
		- br
		- bugzilla
		- ca
		- careers
		- cn
		- de
		- docs
		- engage
		- es
		- (www.)europe	(^ → www)
		- fr
		- gb
		- hardware
		- id
		- in
